Electrum-GRS - lightweight Groestlcoin client

1. GETTING STARTED
------------------
To run Electrum-GRS from this directory, just do:
  ./electrum-grs

If you install Electrum-GRS on your system, you can run it from any directory.
  Install dependencies: sudo apt-get install python-qt4 python-pip
  Install Electrum:  sudo pip install https://github.com/GroestlCoin/electrum-grs/archive/v2.0.3.tar.gz

2. HOW OFFICIAL PACKAGES ARE CREATED
------------------------------------
python mki18n.py
pyrcc4 icons.qrc -o gui/qt/icons_rc.py
python setup.py sdist --format=zip,gztar

On Mac OS X:
  # On port based installs
  sudo python setup-release.py py2app
  # On brew installs
  ARCHFLAGS="-arch i386 -arch x86_64" sudo python setup-release.py py2app --includes sip
  sudo hdiutil create -fs HFS+ -volname "Electrum" -srcfolder dist/Electrum.app dist/electrum-VERSION-macosx.dmg
